high_descs: Step forward, turn right and walk to night stand to the left of the couch.
Pick up the credit card on the right corner of the night stand.
Turn right, step forward, turn right and walk to the end of the room, then hang left and walk to the coffee table. Turn left to face the table edge.
Place the credit card inside the box.
Pick up the box from the table.
Turn around, step forward, turn right and walk to floor shelf.
Place the box in between the salt shaker and the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Place a credit card inside a box and take the box to a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right at the black bench, turn left to the window and walk to the small black table on the right.
Pick up the blue credit card from the right corner of the table.
Turn around, take a left at the black bench and walk to the coffee table on the left.
Put the credit card inside the cardboard box on the table.
Pick up the box with the credit card inside from the table.
Turn around, take a right at the wall and walk to the black bench.
Put the box with the credit card inside on the right side of the bench in between the newspaper and the remote control.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a credit card on a bench.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table to the left of the couch.
Pick up the blue credit card on the table.
Turn around and walk ahead, then left after passing the coffee table to the side of the table with the box.
Place the credit card in the box on the table.
Pick up the box.
Turn left and walk to the black shelf in the corner.
Place the box on the shelf, to the left of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a credit card in it on a shelf.
